claim: The Christmas (film) is based on a song by Whitney Houston.
premise_source_doc_sentence: In honor of its 25th anniversary , the album was reissued as Whitney Houston -- The Deluxe Anniversary Edition on January 26 , 2010 , an expanded edition with five bonus tracks including the a cappella version of `` How Will I Know '' and the original 12-inch remixes , a booklet tracking the history of the original album , along with a DVD of live performances and interviews by Whitney Houston and Clive Davis .
